---
// Testimonials Page
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-background" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:rm6m6e">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8dd">
    <div class="text-center mb-16" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8dc">
      <h1 class="text-[48px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:epiayk">
        Real Couples, <span class="text-primary italic font-normal" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:i0hay0">Real Love Stories</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcov">
        Read firsthand experiences from couples who trusted us to design their dream destination wedding.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8db">
      <!-- Sarah & James -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover-lift" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8da">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8d9">
          <img crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544537732-0858b186c2be?auto=format&w=640&q=80" alt="Sarah & James wedding" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:v53cpj" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-10" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8d8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8d7">
            <div data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8d6">
              <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:enbjgq">Sarah & James</h3>
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcow">September 2023</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:tbqgoz">"The best day of our lives!"</h4>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcox">
            We couldn't have asked for a more perfect wedding. The Wedding Travel Company handled every detail flawlessly. St Raphael Resort was exactly what we dreamed of—the beach setting was stunning and the staff went above and beyond to make our day special. Everything from the welcome drinks to the final dance was magical.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-border pt-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8ck">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcoy">Married at</p>
            <a href="/venues/st-raphael-resort" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:h9f9dy">St Raphael Resort, Cyprus</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Emma & Thomas -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover-lift" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8cj">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8ci">
          <img crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1758810410268-5e9d85b60065?auto=format&w=640&q=80" alt="Emma & Thomas wedding" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:v53cpi" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-10" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8ch">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8cg">
            <div data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8cf">
              <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:enbjgp">Emma & Thomas</h3>
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcoz">August 2023</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:tbqgoy">"A perfect Mediterranean celebration"</h4>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcp0">
            Booking through The Wedding Travel Company was the best decision we made. We were nervous about planning a wedding abroad, but their team made it completely stress-free. The resort provided a breathtaking backdrop for our photos and the sunset reception was incredible. We highly recommend them to any couple!
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-border pt-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8ce">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcp1">Married at</p>
            <a href="/venues/st-raphael-resort/" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:h9f9dz">Alexander The Great Beach Hotel</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Chloe & Michael -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover-lift" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8cd">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8cc">
          <img crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1714972383570-44ddc9738355?auto=format&w=640&q=80" alt="Chloe & Michael wedding" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:v53cph" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-10" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:smu8cb">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmear">
            <div data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmeas">
              <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:enbjgo">Chloe & Michael</h3>
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcp2">June 2023</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:tbqgox">"An unforgettable party under the stars"</h4>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcp3">
            From our very first enquiry to the big day itself, the service was impeccable. Our wedding planner helped us customize every aspect of the day. The beachfront venue was absolutely gorgeous, and having all our friends and family there celebrating with us was a dream come true.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-border pt-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmeat">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcpp">Married at</p>
            <a href="/venues/st-raphael-resort/" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:h9f9e0">Nissi Beach Resort, Cyprus</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Olivia & Daniel -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover-lift" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmeau">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmeav">
          <img crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1768777278961-df45d3c2aa22?auto=format&w=640&q=80" alt="Olivia & Daniel wedding" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:v53cov" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-10" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmeaw">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmeax">
            <div data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmeay">
              <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:enbjgn">Olivia & Daniel</h3>
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcpq">May 2023</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary mb-4" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:tbqgow">"Our absolute dream wedding"</h4>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcpr">
            We wanted a luxurious feel without the stress of coordinating everything ourselves. The team delivered beyond our expectations! The venue we chose was elegant, the food was spectacular, and the dedicated wedding coordinator at the resort made sure we didn't have to worry about a single thing.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-border pt-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmeaz">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcps">Married at</p>
            <a href="/venues/st-raphael-resort/" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:h9f9e1">Olympic Lagoon Resort, Paphos</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Submit Testimonial CTA -->
    <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-12 text-center" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:lzmeb0">
      <h2 class="text-[36px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:13dqz">Did We Plan Your Big Day?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcpt">
        We'd love to hear about your experience and feature your beautiful moments on our site. Share your story, let us know which venue you stayed at, and inspire future couples!
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-[24px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-6" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:enbjgm">Submit Your Testimonial</h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:a5hcpu">
        Email us your review along with a few of your favorite high-resolution photos and the name of your venue to be featured.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:reviews@weddingtravelcompany.com" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[14px] hover:bg-primary-hover transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-primary/20" data-ps="src/components/testimonials/TestimonialsContent.astro:h9f9e2">
        Email Your Review
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>